casebody.data:
No. 09-1314. Charles L. Ryan, Director, Arizona Department of Corrections, Petitioner v. Danny Lee Jones. 563 U.S. 932, 131 S. Ct. 2091,

179 L. Ed. 2d 886,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2987. April 18, 2011.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Cullen v. Pinholster, 563 U.S. 170, 131 S. Ct. 1388, 179 L. Ed. 2d 557 (2011).

Same case below, 583 F.3d 626.
